    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[A new airport has been added to &quot;I am an Air Traffic Controller 4&quot;]</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/b14ef9a5e9c4ed6acffdb7b0ab2a622c.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/4359ee0af90cb1958cf3cea64cbd6023.poster.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/4359ee0af90cb1958cf3cea64cbd6023.webm?t=1756887386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/4359ee0af90cb1958cf3cea64cbd6023.mp4?t=1756887386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Airport Covered]</h2>As Hokkaido’s largest international airport, New Chitose Airport (CTS/RJCC) handles many international and domestic flights.<br>At the adjacent Chitose Air Base are engaged in activities to keep Japan safe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/21a00b2af622f8e106fbbe49dcb28676.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Control two different types of airfields at the same time!]</h2>Many types of airplanes fly into New Chitose Airport, which is used by various domestic and international airlines.<br>In addition, training for fighter planes and the Techno Coast Guard frequently takes place at Chitose Air Base.<br>This game lets you experience the different characteristics of both airfields simultaneously.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/ce393ff60be71c48cb64e2225da3d031.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Enjoy two seasons!]</h2>For the first time, I am an Air Traffic Controller 4 covers both the summer and winter seasons!<br>In the winter stage, runways also close due to snow…<br>Find precious time between crisscrossing flights to issue orders for snow removal on four runways without disrupting operations!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/82ecf1b6dd3d77f1ebfc04c2fbd98d1b.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Key elements to liven up the game]</h2>- F15 fighters fly in single file formation. Take care to maintain sufficient separation between the leader jet and wingman jets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/90779310f227c301e2545e4d2cea30e3.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>- In summer, thick fog from the ocean often hinders visibility. Immobilized aircraft may find it necessary to request a follow-me car.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/550a41a44f805a4e9137ab132a486b1b.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>- Traffic controllers are transported by microbus to and from the control tower during shift changes. The microbus uses taxiways, so the utmost caution is required!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839300/extras/d464c81e061326840ab8cf4c79003960.avif?t=1756887386\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>",
